{
  "stem": "27409.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I recognize some of the faces.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were shot by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not interested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, they were interested in liberate the Ukraine, and they got-- they had a radio station, which I couldn't go to hear.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had the connection with [NON-ENGLISH], the great Earth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a free country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they asked-- with the radio, they asked to drop ammunition or this, about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dropped.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or dropped by plane.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or we had to-- to take them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a time in Berdychiv, was a Slovak unit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The commanding officer was, uh, a connection with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he supplied us with bandages, some [INAUDIBLE], oh, uh, some ammunition.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, he hated the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he also sometimes told-- there is German [INAUDIBLE] with ammunition and food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We go in this direction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we had our connection with him and-- and operated [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't speak, and I didn't ask.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, I could not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would have known.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What is your interest in Jews?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I mean, generally, against Ukrainians or-- or Russians if they--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- those who were with us hated the Germans, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some, uh, had their parents or relatives killed, or they were sent off to labor force and escaped, as I told you before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not friends of the Germans, see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some were, uh, [NON-ENGLISH], this is young communists.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they fought with-- some were party members, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But all of their fighting them, for me, it was-- I saved my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They saved my life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I fought the common enemy, if I could call it like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
